    <stitle>INSTRUMENTS - 1000 SERIES - OPERATION - OIL PRESSURE GAUGE</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="operate" graphiccount="0">
        <title>OIL PRESSURE GAUGE</title>
        <para>The engine oil pressure is sensed by an electrical sending unit that sends a voltage to the ECM2. The ECM2
            converts the electrical voltage into a data signal and transfers it, via the data link, to the
            microprocessor in the instrument cluster. The microprocessor drives the oil pressure gauge.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
